OL,3,CChanges to debt rules would not alter
OL,4,Cthe 'fiscal reality', IFS says
OL,6,FChanging the way debt is measured
OL,7,Fwould allow the Government to borrow
OL,8,Fbillions more but would not change the
OL,9,F"fiscal reality", the Institute for
OL,10,FFiscal Studies (IFS) has said.
OL,12,FIFS senior research economist Ben
OL,13,FZaranko said a change to the debt
OL,14,Frules could be an "attractive" option
OL,15,Ffor Chancellor Rachel Reeves, who has
OL,16,Faccused the previous government of
OL,17,Fleaving #22 billion of unfunded
OL,18,Fcommitments.
