OL,4,Cthe 'fiscal reality', IFS says
OL,6,FBut the think tank said technical
OL,7,Fchanges to definitions would not
OL,8,Fchange the "fiscal reality", and Mr
OL,9,FZaranko warned the Government not to
OL,10,Fget "bogged down in technical debt
OL,11,Fdefinitions".
OL,13,FThis comes after Ms Reeves refused to
OL,14,Frule out debt changes, instead telling
OL,15,Fthe Financial Times earlier this week
OL,16,Fthat the "precise details of the
OL,17,Ffiscal rules" will be published in the
OL,18,FBudget in October.
