OL,3,CChanges to debt rules would not alter
OL,4,Cthe 'fiscal reality', IFS says
OL,6,FMr Zaranko said: "Tweaking the
OL,7,Fdefinition of debt, to allow for
OL,8,Fadditional borrowing without breaching
OL,9,Fthe letter of the fiscal rules, may
OL,10,Fwell be an attractive option for the
OL,11,Fnew Chancellor.
OL,13,F"Such a change would be fairly modest
OL,14,Fand might be sufficiently far into the
OL,15,Ffiscal weeds to avoid any sort of
OL,16,Fadverse reaction from financial
OL,17,Fmarkets. But additional borrowing is
OL,18,Fstill additional borrowing.
