OL,4,Cthe 'fiscal reality', IFS says
OL,6,F"If the Government wants to borrow and
OL,7,Finvest more, there is a coherent and
OL,8,Fprincipled case to be made for doing
OL,9,Fso. Ideally, we would hear that case
OL,10,Fand debate its merits, rather than get
OL,11,Fbogged down in technical debt
OL,12,Fdefinitions and an unhelpful
OL,13,Fdiscussion about so-called fiscal
OL,14,Fheadroom."
OL,16,FOn Monday, Ms Reeves confirmed her
OL,17,FGovernment will "be sticking to"
OL,18,Felection commitments not to raise
OL,19,Fincome tax, national insurance and VAT
OL,20,F"for the duration of this Parliament".
